data.description: Beautiful well kept 3 bedroom 1 bath brick home with an updated modern kitchen, hardwood floor in the living room and bedrooms. Fully finished basement with a wet bar makes for a nice family room, laundry, newer HVAC unit, extra room and lots of storage in the basement. Fully fenced in yard with a detached two car garage. Conveniently located close to shopping malls, good access to all transportation and close to airport. Great opportunity to move into a friendly, nice quiet neighborhood in the heart of Des Plaines.
